1. Split server bootstrap from app export (#9) — enables testability.
2. Add `helmet`, disable `x-powered-by`, add JSON body limits (#2, #3).
3. Add the error-handling + 404 middleware and process-level handlers (#1).
4. Add rate limiting (#4).
5. Add auth + validation scaffolding before `/users` grows (#5, #6).

