```

## 11. Logging & observability

`console.log` isn't structured and has no request context. Use a real logger with request IDs (`pino-http` is lightweight) so you can correlate errors to requests during incidents.

## 12. Graceful shutdown

Add SIGTERM handling so in-flight requests finish before the process exits (important behind load balancers / Kubernetes):

```js
const shutdown = () => server.close(() => process.exit(0));
process.on('SIGTERM', shutdown);
process.on('SIGINT', shutdown);
```

