| Priority | Change | Why |
|---|---|---|
| P0 | Add central error middleware | Prevents stack-trace leaks |
| P0 | Add `helmet` and disable `x-powered-by` | Baseline HTTP hardening |
| P0 | Set `express.json` body limit | Mitigates DoS via large payloads |
| P1 | Add rate limiting | Brute-force / scraping defense |
| P1 | Require auth before `/users` | PII exposure today |
| P1 | Graceful shutdown | Avoid dropped in-flight requests on deploy |
| P2 | Add schema validation library | Ready for first input-taking route |
| P2 | Swap `console` for structured logger (pino/winston) | Observability |

