- [ ] Validation library on every input surface
- [ ] Body-parser size limits
- [ ] `helmet`, rate limiting, CORS allowlist, disable `x-powered-by`
- [ ] Authz + field allowlisting before returning user data
- [ ] Env-var-driven config with validation
- [ ] Graceful shutdown on `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT`
