For container/K8s environments:
```js
const server = app.listen(PORT, /* ... */);
['SIGTERM', 'SIGINT'].forEach((sig) =>
  process.on(sig, () => server.close(() => process.exit(0)))
);
```

## 8. HTTPS/trust proxy

If deployed behind a load balancer, set `app.set('trust proxy', 1)` so `req.ip` and rate-limiting work correctly, and enforce HTTPS at the proxy (HSTS is handled by `helmet`).

