| **Brute force / abuse** | `express-rate-limit` |
| **Invalid/malicious input** | `express-validator` with whitelisted types & bounds |
| **Stack trace leakage** | Centralized error handler that returns generic 500s |
| **Crash on async errors** | `next(err)` pattern + `unhandledRejection`/`uncaughtException` listeners |
| **PII exposure** | Drop `email` from unauthenticated responses |
| **Config in source** | `process.env.PORT` |
| **Abrupt termination** | SIGTERM/SIGINT graceful shutdown |

