| Crash on port conflict | `server.on('error')` handler |
| Unhandled async errors | `process.on('unhandledRejection' / 'uncaughtException')` |
| Abrupt termination | SIGTERM/SIGINT graceful shutdown |
| Misconfigured port | Validate `PORT` is an integer in range |

