Neither endpoint currently accepts input, but the pattern should be in place before `/users/:id`, query params, or a POST is added. Use a schema validator rather than ad hoc checks:

```js
const { z } = require('zod');

const UserIdParams = z.object({ id: z.coerce.number().int().positive() });

app.get('/users/:id', (req, res, next) => {
  const parsed = UserIdParams.safeParse(req.params);
