  if (!parsed.success) {
    return res.status(400).json({ error: 'Invalid user id' });
  }
  // ...
});
```

Validation principles: **allowlist, don't blocklist**; coerce types explicitly; reject on failure rather than sanitize silently.

## 3. Security Headers & Hardening

Add standard protections:

