The file is small (22 lines, two GET endpoints), but it already exhibits several gaps that matter as soon as it grows beyond a toy. Here are concrete improvements, ordered by priority.

## 1. No global error handler (high priority)

Express will leak stack traces to the client in development mode, and unhandled errors in async routes will crash the process. Add a final error-handling middleware and `process` guards.

```js
